snippet.title: Skystrider | Trailer Breakdown
snippet.description:
A look at the storyboarding behind the trailer for Skystrider!

Skystrider is a 3-D Action Platformer. As a resurrected hero, explore a ruined world, navigating perilous paths amidst clouds and tides. Unleash ancient technology to open the way. 

🞛 Wishlist on Steam! A playable demo is coming December 2023 🞛
https://store.steampowered.com
/app/2434450/Skystrider/

🞛 Follow us on Twitter @ studioichor 🞛

Music credit - Scott Buckley https://www.scottbuckley.com.au/
Voice credit - Francesca Mintowt-Czyz
Storyboard Artists - Kelly Alexander and John Arters
